{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0143v2QXh2jTeshrVXPivYY6","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nI have successfully written all 6 Spring Boot REST controller files for the migration. Here's what was created:\n\n### Files Written:\n\n1. **ArticlesResource.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java`\n   - Converted from JAX-RS to Spring MVC with `@RestController` and `@RequestMapping`\n   - Changed JAX-RS annotations (`@GET`, `@POST`, `@PUT`, `@DELETE`, `@Path`, `@QueryParam`, `@PathParam`) to Spring equivalents (`@GetMapping`, `@PostMapping`, `@PutMapping`, `@DeleteMapping`, `@RequestParam`, `@PathVariable`)\n   - Replaced `SecurityContext` with Spring's `Principal` for user authentication\n   - Changed return types from `Response` to `ResponseEntity`\n\n2. **ProfilesResource.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java`\n   - Migrated to Spring MVC annotations\n   - Uses `Principal` instead of `SecurityContext`\n\n3. **TagsResource.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/TagsResource.java`\n   - Simple GET endpoint converted to Spring MVC\n\n4. **UserResource.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java`\n   - GET and PUT endpoints migrated to Spring annotations\n   - Uses `Principal` for authentication\n\n5. **UsersResource.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java`\n   - Converted user registration and login endpoints\n   - Changed `UnauthorizedException` to Spring's `BadCredentialsException`\n\n6. **ResourceUtils.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java`\n   - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` to `@Component` for Spring dependency injection\n   - Modified `getLoggedUserId()` to accept `Principal` instead of `SecurityContext`\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated from Quarkus/JAX-RS to Spring Boot/Spring MVC framework."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"77854f62-3341-42f0-ba47-aba7925f4b32","uuid":"f1510040-8b03-4f50-b11d-b7a81c5bd020"}
