{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VhW2FHGUAKMzAk3BBrxJib","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully written all 8 repository files for the Spring Boot migration from Quarkus Panache. Here's a summary of what was completed:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nAll repository files have been successfully migrated from Quarkus Panache to Spring Boot with JPA EntityManager. The key changes include:\n\n### Files Written:\n\n1. **ArticleRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/ArticleRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Implements complex article filtering with dynamic HQL queries\n   - Uses EntityManager for pagination and counting\n\n2. **CommentRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/CommentRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Handles comment CRUD operations with EntityManager\n\n3. **FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Manages favorite relationships with composite key lookups\n\n4. **FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Handles user follow relationships with composite keys\n\n5. **TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Manages article-tag relationships\n\n6. **TagRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Handles tag CRUD operations\n\n7. **UserRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/UserRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Manages user entities with case-insensitive lookups\n\n8. **AbstractPanacheRepository.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/AbstractPanacheRepository.java`\n   - Emptied as it's no longer needed (previously extended Panache base)\n\n### Key Migration Changes:\n\n- **Removed Panache dependencies**: No longer extends `AbstractPanacheRepository` or uses Panache-specific methods\n- **Added Spring annotations**: `@Repository` instead of `@ApplicationScoped`\n- **Added EntityManager injection**: Using `@PersistenceContext` for JPA EntityManager\n- **Constructor injection**: Changed from Lombok's `@AllArgsConstructor` to explicit constructor for EntityUtils\n- **Direct HQL queries**: All Panache helper methods replaced with `entityManager.createQuery()`\n- **Manual parameter binding**: Using `setParameter()` instead of Panache's Parameters API\n- **Explicit pagination**: Using `setFirstResult()` and `setMaxResults()` instead of Panache's `Page` API\n- **Manual entity lookups**: Using `entityManager.find()` instead of `findById()` or similar Panache methods\n\nAll repositories now use pure JPA EntityManager with HQL queries, making them compatible with Spring Boot while maintaining the same business logic and query functionality."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"77854f62-3341-42f0-ba47-aba7925f4b32","uuid":"e592fbcb-9f70-4f59-9322-1193e4673561"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_014oBGj3kF5KE929Ufi2do2z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_012osDhRMW6PZcBHQEM9ADAN","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/ExceptionMappers.java","content":"package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.mapper;\n\nimport jakarta.validation.ConstraintViolationException;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.application.web.model.response.ErrorResponse;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.exception.*;\nimport org.springframework.http.HttpStatus;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.security.authentication.BadCredentialsException;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.MethodArgumentNotValidException;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.ExceptionHandler;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RestControllerAdvice;\n\n@RestControllerAdvice\npublic class ExceptionMappers {\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(BadCredentialsException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> unauthorized(BadCredentialsException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.UNAUTHORIZED)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(\"Unauthorized\"));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(EmailAlreadyExistsException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> emailAlreadyExists(EmailAlreadyExistsException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.CONFLICT)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(e.getMessage()));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(UsernameAlreadyExistsException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> usernameAlreadyExists(UsernameAlreadyExistsException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.CONFLICT)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(e.getMessage()));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(UserNotFoundException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> userNotFound(UserNotFoundException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(e.getMessage()));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(InvalidPasswordException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> invalidPassword(InvalidPasswordException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.UNAUTHORIZED)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(e.getMessage()));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(TagNotFoundException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> tagNotFound(TagNotFoundException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(e.getMessage()));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(ArticleNotFoundException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> articleNotFound(ArticleNotFoundException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(e.getMessage()));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(ModelValidationException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> modelValidation(ModelValidationException e) {\n    return ResponseEntity.status(422)\n        .body(new ErrorResponse(e.getMessage()));\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(ConstraintViolationException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> constraintViolation(ConstraintViolationException e) {\n    ErrorResponse errorResponse = new ErrorResponse();\n    e.getConstraintViolations()\n        .iterator()\n        .forEachRemaining(constraint -> errorResponse.getBody().add(constraint.getMessage()));\n    return ResponseEntity.status(422).body(errorResponse);\n  }\n\n  @ExceptionHandler(MethodArgumentNotValidException.class)\n  public ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse> methodArgumentNotValid(MethodArgumentNotValidException e) {\n    ErrorResponse errorResponse = new ErrorResponse();\n    e.getBindingResult().getAllErrors()\n        .forEach(error -> errorResponse.getBody().add(error.getDefaultMessage()));\n    return ResponseEntity.status(422).body(errorResponse);\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4786,"cache_read_input_tokens":36548,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4786,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4855},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01X2xK2TdkPMxMKJwrdZXJv9","session_id":"77854f62-3341-42f0-ba47-aba7925f4b32","uuid":"5b865f2a-4aa3-47b5-8ccc-79366d8b1a2b"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_014oBGj3kF5KE929Ufi2do2z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_016KtvqLZ4gcsW4Mm2CsSs5P","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java","content":"package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.mapper;\n\n// This class is no longer needed - bean validation exceptions are handled by ExceptionMappers.\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4786,"cache_read_input_tokens":36548,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4786,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4855},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01X2xK2TdkPMxMKJwrdZXJv9","session_id":"77854f62-3341-42f0-ba47-aba7925f4b32","uuid":"3be83501-21fd-429f-91b3-e18abc61b82a"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_014oBGj3kF5KE929Ufi2do2z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01CLQjrCLxSJqCUSzQqPpgWR","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java","content":"package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity;\n\nimport lombok.AllArgsConstructor;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.Article;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.ArticleModelBuilder;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.FavoriteRelationship;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.comment.Comment;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.comment.CommentBuilder;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.tag.Tag;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.tag.TagBuilder;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.User;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.UserModelBuilder;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\n@Component\n@AllArgsConstructor\npublic class EntityUtils {\n  private final UserModelBuilder userBuilder;\n  private final TagBuilder tagBuilder;\n  private final ArticleModelBuilder articleBuilder;\n  private final CommentBuilder commentBuilder;\n\n  public User user(UserEntity userEntity) {\n    final var id = userEntity.getId();\n    final var username = userEntity.getUsername();\n    final var bio = userEntity.getBio();\n    final var image = userEntity.getImage();\n    final var password = userEntity.getPassword();\n    final var email = userEntity.getEmail();\n    return userBuilder.build(id, username, bio, image, password, email);\n  }\n\n  public Tag tag(TagEntity tagEntity) {\n    return tagBuilder.build(tagEntity.getId(), tagEntity.getName());\n  }\n\n  public Tag tag(TagRelationshipEntity tagRelationshipEntity) {\n    return tag(tagRelationshipEntity.getPrimaryKey().getTag());\n  }\n\n  public Article article(ArticleEntity articleEntity) {\n    return articleBuilder.build(\n        articleEntity.getId(),\n        articleEntity.getSlug(),\n        articleEntity.getTitle(),\n        articleEntity.getDescription(),\n        articleEntity.getBody(),\n        articleEntity.getCreatedAt(),\n        articleEntity.getUpdatedAt(),\n        user(articleEntity.getAuthor()));\n  }\n\n  public Comment comment(CommentEntity commentEntity) {\n    return commentBuilder.build(\n        commentEntity.getId(),\n        user(commentEntity.getAuthor()),\n        article(commentEntity.getArticle()),\n        commentEntity.getBody(),\n        commentEntity.getCreatedAt(),\n        commentEntity.getUpdatedAt());\n  }\n\n  public FavoriteRelationship favoriteRelationship(\n      FavoriteRelationshipEntity favoriteRelationshipEntity) {\n    return new FavoriteRelationship(\n        user(favoriteRelationshipEntity.getUser()),\n        article(favoriteRelationshipEntity.getArticle()));\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4786,"cache_read_input_tokens":36548,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4786,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4855},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01X2xK2TdkPMxMKJwrdZXJv9","session_id":"77854f62-3341-42f0-ba47-aba7925f4b32","uuid":"5e0286fa-40aa-4068-8ace-4c7c757c60a0"}
